{"name": "ocpiupdate", "metadata": {"name": "ocpiupdate", "version": "0.1.2", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "An updater for OpenCPI Projects", "upload_time": 1732225900}, "documentation": ["# ocpiupdate - An updater for OpenCPI Projects\n\n`ocpiupdate` automatically updated OpenCPI Projects to use the semantics\nassociated with newer versions of OpenCPI.\n\nFor example:\n\n- Using `<worker>-<model>.xml` for the OWD files, instead of `<worker>.xml`.\n- Using `<component>.comp/<component>-comp.xml` for OCS files instead of\n  `specs/<component>[-_]spec.xml`.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "ocpiupdate.v2_4_7_updater", "documentation": ["!/usr/bin/env python3"], "functions": [{"name": "ocpiupdate.v2_4_7_updater.yield_workers_from_library", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "library_directory", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Yield a generator of worker directory paths from a library path."]}, {"name": "ocpiupdate.v2_4_7_updater.yield_specs_from_library", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "library_directory", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Yield a generator of spec file paths from a library path."]}, {"name": "ocpiupdate.v2_4_7_updater.recursive_findall", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "element", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "tag", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Find all occurrences of a given XML tag at any depth in an XML tree."]}, {"name": "ocpiupdate.v2_4_7_updater.v2_4_7_owd_rename", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "worker_directory", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "version_to", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Rename all OWD files to their v2.4.7 names.\n\n- Move all *.hdl/*.xml to *.hdl/*-hdl.xml\n- Move all *.rcc/*.xml to *.rcc/*-rcc.xml\n    - This isn't done for RCC Workers th